  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n#### [Design](https://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/KubaâŽœDesktop?type=design&node-id=36746-623205&mode=design&t=NJrbLCMyceZK5Oea-0)\r\n\r\nThe design for Community Membership Settings page has been updated to better indicate the `accept pending` and `reject pending` states of a community membership request when the control node is offline.\r\n\r\nThis task is to create the new `accept pending` and `reject pending` indicators based on backend state. When a membership request is in accept/reject pending, the admin that initiated the state change can still use the other actions to toggle the membership request between Accept pending and Reject pending until the control node is back online.\r\n\r\nWhen the request is in pending state, the actions are visible only on hover.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"429\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-08-16 at 09 15 22\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/47811206/c71e6622-0109-4377-b53c-d8e44e772c94\">\r\n\r\n",
